-- Yuan Exchange Rate Needs Flexibility, News Says, Citing Central Bank Aide
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-04-28T00:04:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-28/yuan-exchange-rate-needs-flexibility-news-says-citing-central-bank-aide.html

          
          
             China’s foreign exchange rate and
interest rates should be kept “appropriately” flexible,
Shanghai Securities News reported Zhou Qiren, a central bank
advisor, saying at a conference yesterday.  
 Banks should be prepared for flexible changes in monetary
policy over the next two years, the report said.  
